{"tid":24136,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[晴報]80後寧做車房，不做IT人！！","createTime":"2016-12-05T11:18:22.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T14:52:37.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e6da327e9a2e1222721219bebfb73b19a8923303","tid":24136,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:18:22.000Z","msg":"【晴報專訊】2013年於中大系統工程與工程管理學系畢業。他一直懷着創業的夢想，初出茅廬就以約1萬元編寫了一個專為freelance招聘的網站，但因欠缺宣傳，3個月後失敗告終，「當時迷失在悲傷足足一個月，但後來想通了，以正面態度面對失敗。」 <br />\n<br />\n因父親有40年輪胎業經驗，鍾浩賢認為做生不如做熟，毅然以60萬買回父親已頂讓的輪胎店。 <br />\n創業的路很難走，他每天工作逾11小時，更由「白領」變「藍領」，常要落手落腳搬運重達40公斤的車胎，體力以外，還要腦力，另再花2至3小時編寫程式及擬定工作計劃，「創業就預了長時間工作，預咗要孤獨，也要有心理準備會失敗。」他仍抱正面心態，「期望明年中達收支平衡。」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/20160901/001/%E6%8D%A8Office%E5%B7%A5%E8%AE%8A%E8%BB%8A%E6%88%BF%E4%BB%94+80%E5%BE%8CIT%E4%BA%BA%E6%B1%BA%E5%BF%83%E6%95%B4App%E5%89%B5%E8%B2%A1%E8%B7%AF/227812\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2F20160901%2F001%2F%25E6%258D%25A8Office%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%25AE%258A%25E8%25BB%258A%25E6%2588%25BF%25E4%25BB%2594%2B80%25E5%25BE%258CIT%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%25BF%2583%25E6%2595%25B4App%25E5%2589%25B5%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E8%25B7%25AF%2F227812&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69Av3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=a304017a\" target=\"_blank\">http://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/20160901/001/%E6%8D%A8Office%E5%B7%A5%E8%AE%8A%E8%BB%8A%E6%88%BF%E4%BB%94+80%E5%BE%8CIT%E4%BA%BA%E6%B1%BA%E5%BF%83%E6%95%B4App%E5%89%B5%E8%B2%A1%E8%B7%AF/227812</a><br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"http://app03.skypost.hk/fileData/iphone/data/20160901/001/sksinn20160822211_20160901_L.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fapp03.skypost.hk%2FfileData%2Fiphone%2Fdata%2F20160901%2F001%2Fsksinn20160822211_20160901_L.jpg&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69Av3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=d9ece12a\